The paper focuses on deep learning for face attribute prediction, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The use of cascaded CNNs and pre-training strategies also suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper deals with image and video processing (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR) in the context of face attribute prediction.
